Liverpool manager Brendan Rodgers will have to plan without the French centre-back with a hamstring injury .
Sakho limped off the field during Liverpool 's FA Cup quarter-final victory against Blackburn Rovers on Wednesday and was replaced by Kolo Toure in the 28th minute .
The Sakho will sit out his side 's clash against Newcastle United at Anfield on Monday night and is set to miss the FA Cup semi-final showdown with Aston Villa on Monday .